"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The White House says Donald Trump is happy with the blockade of Iran's ports. Tehran's top negotiator says this breaks the ceasefire.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump and Iran Blockade\",            \"translated_version\": \"La Casa Blanca dice que Donald Trump est\u00e1 feliz con el bloqueo de los puertos de Ir\u00e1n. El negociador de Teher\u00e1n dice que esto rompe el alto el fuego.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump y Bloqueo de Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Zambia authorities and Edgar Lungu's family are arguing about where the former leader's body should be buried.\",            \"english_title\": \"Zambia Burial Dispute\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las autoridades de Zambia y la familia de Edgar Lungu est\u00e1n discutiendo sobre d\u00f3nde debe ser enterrado el cuerpo del exl\u00edder.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Disputa de Entierro en Zambia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pope gives a strong and emotional speech during his tour of Africa.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pope's Speech in Africa\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Papa da un discurso fuerte y emocional durante su gira por \u00c1frica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Discurso del Papa en \u00c1frica\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Lebanon's prime minister says Israel committed war crimes after attacks on Red Cross vehicles stopped rescuers from reaching the site.\",            \"english_title\": \"Lebanon Accuses Israel\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de L\u00edbano dice que Israel cometi\u00f3 cr\u00edmenes de guerra despu\u00e9s de que los ataques a veh\u00edculos de la Cruz Roja impidieron que los rescatistas llegaran al lugar.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edbano Acusa a Israel\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine says it has reopened the Druzhba pipeline after months of no oil supplies to Hungary.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Reopens Pipeline\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ucrania dice que ha reabierto el oleoducto Druzhba despu\u00e9s de meses sin suministros de petr\u00f3leo a Hungr\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Reabre Oleoducto\"        }    ]}"